     C*
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C*
     C                     WRITEFMT099
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDW@RCN3    #RCN03
     C                     EXFMTCTL030
     C   KC
     COR KL                LEAVE
     C*
     C           @@REC     IFNE *ZERO
     C                     Z-ADD@@REC     W@RCN3
